    "description": "An Italian classic every Nonna would be proud of. You'll coat steak in a crisp herb and cheese crumb, then pan-fry until golden. Serve with rosemary potatoes and lemon-caper broccoli for a Milanese that's crisp, fresh and satisfying.",
